data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cjd1665702650499.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cjd1665702650499.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cjd1665702650499.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cjd1665702650499\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Orientation of the widget, vertical or horizontal.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__p_d106313e1_d106314e1_d106315e1\">Orientation<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">V</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">H</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__2\">Representation</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__2\">\n (default)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__3\">Use the setting specified in the\n                        <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">V</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__2\">Vertical </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__3\">Widget is vertical. Default system orientation for\n                     spin button.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">H</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__2\">\n Horizontal\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12548e1_d12549e1_d12550e1__entry__3\">Widget is horizontal. Default system orientation\n                     for slider.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__section_x5b_b43_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d632994e137\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__table_d12551e1_d12552e1_d12553e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes, except for progress bar</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__section_j5v_g43_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d632994e183\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__p_d106322e1_d106323e1_d106324e1\">For spin buttons, the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Orientation</span> property determines whether the arrow buttons are\n            positioned above each other (Vertical) or beside each other (Horizontal).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__p_d106325e1_d106326e1_d106327e1\">For sliders and progress bars, the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Orientation</span> property determines whether the slider is drawn\n            from left to right (Horizontal) or from bottom top (Vertical).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__p_d106328e1_d106329e1_d106330e1\">For progress bars, this widget is static and cannot\n            be changed in ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__section_fyh_343_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d632994e204\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__pre_h2x_j43_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"orientation=h\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__section_bqb_k43_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d632994e214\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__ul_zgd_l43_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__li_d42077e1_d42078e1_d42079e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qxp1665702650348.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qxp1665702650348.html\" title=\"The uprogressbar is a field-level widget the shows the progress of a process or action that is being executed. Is can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ProgressBar, which is mapped to uprogressbar.\">uprogressbar (ProgressBar)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__li_d42080e1_d42081e1_d42082e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"foe1665702651174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/foe1665702651174.html\" title=\"The uslider widget allows users to edit a numeric value in a field by sliding an indicator in a set of a previously defined range of values. Uniface provides a logical widget called Slider, which is mapped to uslider.\">uslider (Slider)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"cjd1665702650499__li_d42083e1_d42084e1_d42085e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612369\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612369\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Orientation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 11, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Orientation of the widget, vertical or horizontal. Orientation = \" V | H \" Value Representation Description (default) Use the setting specified in the .ini file. V Vertical Widget is vertical. Default system orientation for spin button. H Horizontal Widget is horizontal. Default system orientation for slider. Usage Dynamic? Yes, except for progress bar Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description For spin buttons, the Orientation property determines whether the arrow buttons are positioned above each other (Vertical) or beside each other (Horizontal). For sliders and progress bars, the Orientation property determines whether the slider is drawn from left to right (Horizontal) or from bottom top (Vertical). For progress bars, this widget is static and cannot be changed in ProcScript. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"orientation=h\" Copy Applies To uprogressbar (ProgressBar) uslider (Slider) uspinbutton (SpinButton) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}